parameters.name: SourceDatasetArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the dataset to import.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the request. If you do not set the client request token, Amazon Lookout for Equipment generates one. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: Any tags associated with the dataset to be created. (dict) --- A tag is a key-value pair that can be added to a resource as metadata. The key for the specified tag. The value for the specified tag.

nested_params.name: Key
nested_params.description: The key for the specified tag.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: The value for the specified tag.

nested_items.name: DatasetName
nested_items.description: The name of the created machine learning dataset.

nested_items.name: DatasetArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the dataset that was imported.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the ImportDataset operation.

nested_items.name: JobId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the job of importing the dataset.
